    "title": {
      "rendered": "10 Facebook Page Best Practices for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-16805\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"Facebook Pages Best Practices\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Pages-Best-Practices.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>With more than 1 billion active users, Facebook is the largest social network in the world. More than two-thirds of its users log in every day and three-fourths do so on a mobile device. Without a doubt your nonprofit\u2019s supporters use Facebook on a regular basis. Therefore, Facebook Pages should be your first priority and entry into social networking. but\u00a0to stand out from the other 50 million pages regularly active and all vying for likes, comments, and shares, you must\u00a0excel at Facebook in order to stand out from the clutter and the 10 best practices below will ensure your nonprofit is on the right path.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>1. Invest in quality graphic design for your Avatar (a.k.a. Profile Picture), Timeline Cover, and Tab Icons.</h2>\n<p>First impressions are very important on social networks. To maximize the Likes of your page, invest in quality graphic design.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bestfriendsanimalsociety\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16734\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS1.png?resize=600%2C282\" alt=\"BFAS1\" width=\"600\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS1.png?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bestfriendsanimalsociety\">facebook.com/bestfriendsanimalsociety</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bestfriendsanimalsociety\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16735\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS2.png?resize=600%2C220\" alt=\"BFAS2\" width=\"600\" height=\"220\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/BFAS2.png?resize=300%2C110&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>2. Turn on &#8220;Similar Page Suggestions&#8221; to increase your Likes.</h2>\n<p>Under Settings\u00a0&gt; Similar Page Suggestions, tic the box to include your page when Facebook recommends similar pages. This simple tweak could become your greatest source of new Likes.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16775\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/page-recommendations.png?resize=600%2C342\" alt=\"page recommendations\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/page-recommendations.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/page-recommendations.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden\">facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16737\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Settings.png?resize=600%2C282\" alt=\"Settings\" width=\"600\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Settings.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Settings.png?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>3. Post on Saturday and Sunday mornings using the native scheduling function.</h2>\n<p>Engagement is highest on Saturday and Sunday mornings and thanks to Facebook&#8217;s native scheduling function your nonprofit can easily schedule weekend posts in advance.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16740\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Scheduling.png?resize=532%2C233\" alt=\"Scheduling\" width=\"532\" height=\"233\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Scheduling.png?w=532&amp;ssl=1 532w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Scheduling.png?resize=300%2C131&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>4. Prioritize uploading photos over posting links.</h2>\n<p>Research\u00a0consistently demonstrates that photos receive\u00a0more engagement than any other type of post\u00a0\u2013 despite Facebook&#8217;s insistence otherwise.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/fb_type_likes_months1.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16786\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/fb_type_likes_months1.jpg?resize=532%2C561\" alt=\"fb_type_likes_months\" width=\"532\" height=\"561\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/fb_type_likes_months1.jpg?w=532&amp;ssl=1 532w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/fb_type_likes_months1.jpg?resize=284%2C300&amp;ssl=1 284w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>5. Occasionally &#8220;Pin to Top&#8221; popular Updates.</h2>\n<p>To bring attention to popular and important posts already shared, pin it to the top of your page.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16742\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-1.png?resize=532%2C483\" alt=\"Pin to Top 1\" width=\"532\" height=\"483\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-1.png?w=532&amp;ssl=1 532w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-1.png?resize=300%2C272&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" /></a></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\">facebook.com/nonprofitorgs</a></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16743\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-2.png?resize=532%2C513\" alt=\"Pin to Top 2\" width=\"532\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-2.png?w=532&amp;ssl=1 532w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Pin-to-Top-2.png?resize=300%2C289&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>6. Enable fans to send you direct messages.</h2>\n<p>If your nonprofit has the capacity to engage with fans via direct messages, turn on the messaging functionality in your settings.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whales.org\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16761\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Whales.png?resize=600%2C284\" alt=\"Whales\" width=\"600\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Whales.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Whales.png?resize=300%2C142&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whales.org\">facebook.com/whales.org</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16764\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Messages1.png?resize=600%2C202\" alt=\"Messages\" width=\"600\" height=\"202\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Messages1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Messages1.png?resize=300%2C101&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>7. Have more than one Admin for your Page.</h2>\n<p>To protect your nonprofit from losing access to its page, have at least two Admins with full privileges. You can view the administrative privileges of various roles <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/help/323502271070625\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16767\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Admin.png?resize=600%2C258\" alt=\"Facebook Admin\" width=\"600\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Admin.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Facebook-Admin.png?resize=300%2C129&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>8. Add an address to your page to add Facebook Location.</h2>\n<p>To enable fans to check-in to your page and thus share your page with their fans when they check-in, add your physical address to your page</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16769\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Missouri-Botanical-Garden.png?resize=600%2C383\" alt=\"Missouri Botanical Garden\" width=\"600\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Missouri-Botanical-Garden.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Missouri-Botanical-Garden.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-16770\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/check-in-287x300.png?resize=287%2C300\" alt=\"check in\" width=\"287\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/check-in.png?resize=287%2C300&amp;ssl=1 287w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/check-in.png?w=450&amp;ssl=1 450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 287px) 100vw, 287px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden\">facebook.com/missouribotanicalgarden</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16771\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Address.png?resize=600%2C176\" alt=\"Address\" width=\"600\" height=\"176\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Address.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Address.png?resize=300%2C88&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>9. Add Facebook icons to your website and/or and e-newsletter.</h2>\n<p>To increase the Likes of your page, prominently feature Facebook icons above the fold on your website and/or blog and e-newsletter.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16778\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-blog.png?resize=600%2C254\" alt=\"icons on blog\" width=\"600\" height=\"254\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-blog.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-blog.png?resize=300%2C127&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16779\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-enewsletter.png?resize=600%2C348\" alt=\"icons on enewsletter\" width=\"600\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-enewsletter.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/icons-on-enewsletter.png?resize=300%2C174&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2>10. Experiment with Facebook Events.</h2>\n<p>When fans RSVP &#8220;Join&#8221; to a Facebook Event, the event is added to their Facebook calendar and fans are also notified the day of the event to increase attendance. Be sure to add a link to your Facebook Event when promoting events on your website and/or blog and e-newsletter to increase RSVPs.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightscampaign/events\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16768\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/HRC-Campaign-JPEG.jpg?resize=600%2C404\" alt=\"HRC Campaign JPEG\" width=\"600\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/HRC-Campaign-JPEG.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/HRC-Campaign-JPEG.jpg?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightscampaign/events\">facebook.com/humanrightscampaign/events</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightscampaign/events\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16784\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/facebook-events.png?resize=600%2C336\" alt=\"facebook events\" width=\"600\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/facebook-events.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/facebook-events.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
